<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Your Tour is Coming Up Soon!</h1>

    <p>Dear <%= @booking.booked_name %>,</p>

    <p>
      This is a friendly reminder that your tour "<strong><%= @tour.title %></strong>"
      is coming up in <strong><%= @days_until %> <%= @days_until == 1 ? 'day' : 'days' %></strong>!
    </p>

    <h2>Tour Details:</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Tour:</strong> <%= @tour.title %></li>
      <li><strong>Date & Time:</strong> <%= @tour.starts_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p") %></li>
      <li><strong>Duration:</strong> <%= (@tour.duration_minutes / 60.0).round(1) %> hours</li>
      <li><strong>Meeting Location:</strong> <%= @tour.location_name %></li>
      <li><strong>Number of Participants:</strong> <%= @booking.spots %></li>
      <li><strong>Guide:</strong> <%= @tour.guide.name %></li>
    </ul>

    <% if @booking.booking_add_ons.any? %>
      <h2>Your Add-ons:</h2>
      <ul>
        <% @booking.booking_add_ons.each do |booking_add_on| %>
          <li><%= booking_add_on.tour_add_on.name %></li>
        <% end %>
      </ul>
    <% end %>

    <h2>Before You Go:</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Arrive 10-15 minutes early</strong> at the meeting location</li>
      <li>Check the weather forecast and <strong>dress appropriately</strong></li>
      <li>Bring <strong>comfortable walking shoes</strong></li>
      <li>Don't forget your <strong>water and snacks</strong></li>
      <li>Bring a <strong>camera</strong> to capture the memories</li>
      <% if @days_until == 1 %>
        <li>Make sure your phone is <strong>charged</strong> for photos and navigation</li>
      <% end %>
    </ul>

    <p>
      <strong>Need to make changes?</strong><br/>
      <a href="<%= manage_booking_url(@booking, email: @booking.booked_email) %>"
         style="color: #3182ce;">Manage My Booking</a>
    </p>

    <p>
      We're looking forward to seeing you and providing an unforgettable experience!
    </p>

    <p>
      Best regards,<br/>
      The Tour Team
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
